import React from 'react';
import { Box,  Grid, OutlinedInput } from '@material-ui/core';

export const VerificationCode = (props: {
    valueFirstOTP: string,
    valueSecondOTP: string,
    valueThirdOTP: string,
    valueFourOTP: string,
    valueFiveOTP: string,
    valueSixOTP: string,
    changeInputFirst: () => {},
    changeInputSecond: () => {},
    changeInputFour: () => {},
    changeInputFive: () => {},
    changeInputSix: () => {}
}) => {
    return (
        <Box mt="20px">
            <Grid container>
                <Grid item md={4}>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                    <Grid container>
                        <Grid item xs={2} md={2}>
                            <Box>
                                <OutlinedInput value={props.valueFirstOTP} onChange={changeInputFirst} />
                            </Box>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={2} md={2}>
                            <Box ml="5px">
                                <OutlinedInput value={props.valueSecondOTP} onChange={changeInputSecond} />
                            </Box>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={2} md={2}>
                            <Box ml="5px">
                                <OutlinedInput value={props.valueThirdOTP} onChange={changeInputThird} />
                            </Box>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={2} md={2}>
                            <Box ml="5px">
                                <OutlinedInput value={props.valueFourOTP} onChange={changeInputFour} />
                            </Box>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={2} md={2}>
                            <Box ml="5px">
                                <OutlinedInput value={props.valueFiveOTP} onChange={changeInputFive} />
                            </Box>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={2} md={2}>
                            <Box ml="5px">
                                <OutlinedInput value={props.valueSixOTP} onChange={changeInputSix} />
                            </Box>
                        </Grid>
                        {errorOTP.errorValidNumber !== '' && <Box display="flex" justifyContent="center" width="100%" marginTop="10px" alignItems="center" color="red">{errorOTP.errorValidNumber}</Box>}
                        {errorOTP.errorNullOTP !== '' && <Box display="flex" justifyContent="center" width="100%" marginTop="10px" alignItems="center" color="red">{errorOTP.errorNullOTP}</Box>}
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>

        </Box>
    )
}
